data.eml:eml: Six new species of the brine shrimp Parartemia Sayce 1903 (Crustacea: Anostraca: Artemiina) in Western Australia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Timms, Brian V (2010): Six new species of the brine shrimp Parartemia Sayce 1903 (Crustacea: Anostraca: Artemiina) in Western Australia. Zootaxa 2715: 1-35, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.199709
